</article>
</div>
<h3>BuildOn: Super-specific</h3>
<p>Consider something like this if you&#8217;re a nonprofit.</p>
<ul>
<li>Just the right amount of gratitude and inspiration</li>
<li>Visual with smiling face</li>
<li>Shares specific achievements made possible by YOU</li>
</ul>
<div data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="92f7d2a7-fc67-4f66-aac4-9ec43a125827" data-langcode="en" class="embedded-entity align-center">
