<h3>Later: Future-focused</h3>
<p>The thank you section of Later’s 2020 December newsletter is one to model after.</p>
<ul>
<li>Conversational tone, with emojis</li>
<li>Specific thank yous</li>
<li>Future-focused</li>
<li>Has a CTA, but just to Instagram profile</li>
</ul>
<div data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="ee48e337-6c53-44b8-bdce-54d18f6b699c" data-langcode="en" class="embedded-entity align-center">
<article>
<div><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/holiday-customer-appreciation-message-example-later.png" alt="Later's holiday customer appreciation email example" typeof="foaf:Image" width="550" height="529" /></div>
</article>
